df(x_{t})=\nabla f(x_{t})^{\top}dx_{t}+\frac{1}{2}(dx_{t})^{\top}\nabla^{2}f(x_{t})(dx_{t})=\nabla f(x_{t})^{\top}\mu(x_{t})dt+\nabla f(x_{t})^{\top}\sigma(x_{t})dW_{t}+\frac{1}{2}\tr(\sigma(x_{t})^{\top}\nabla^{2}f(x_{t})\sigma(x_{t}))dt.
